Therefore, it is better to exit with the @SA and a small spade. Switching to a small spade is reasonable play too but you might find yourself end-played later on in the play. Besides, there's a very small chance that partner might have the @HA to give you a spade ruff, so it is better to shorten yourself in spades.|
